name: AVAssetReaderVideoCompositionOutput
desc: An object that reads composited video frames from one or more tracks of an asset.

items.name: init(videoTracks: [AVAssetTrack], videoSettings: [String : Any]?)
items.desc: Creates an object that reads composited video frames from the specified video tracks.

items.name: var videoComposition: AVVideoComposition?
items.desc: The video composition to use for the output.

items.name: var customVideoCompositor: AVVideoCompositing?
items.desc: A custom video compositor for the output.

items.name: var videoTracks: [AVAssetTrack]
items.desc: The tracks from which the output reads the composited video.

items.name: var videoSettings: [String : Any]?
items.desc: The video settings that the output uses.
